name: extreme_with_binding_over_direct_helper_mix
section: binding-scope-deep
args: a:Int b:Int c:Int
type: Bool
expect: True
description: Lexical binding and shadowing must preserve dependency order and branch-local scope.
law: (with [x (fuzz-add {a} {b})] (with [y (+ x {c})] (= y (+ (+ {a} {b}) {c}))))
